#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.18:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Sāraṇīyavagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Macchabandhasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.18:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ carati mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ."
msgstr ""

# Note the repetitive idiom macchika maccabandha, repeated below. Also note the syntax. BB has the more economical “killing fish and selling them”, but I think the repetitive vadhitva vadhitva is meant to emphasize the fact that he killed them himself.
msgctxt "an6.18:1.2"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho bhagavā addhānamaggappaṭipanno aññatarasmiṃ padese macchikaṃ "
"macchabandhaṃ macche vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamānaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:1.3"
msgid "Disvā maggā okkamma aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:1.4"
msgid "Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:1.5"
msgid ""
"“passatha no tumhe, bhikkhave, amuṃ macchikaṃ macchabandhaṃ macche vadhitvā "
"vadhitvā vikkiṇamānan”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:1.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.302"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.18:2.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.2"
msgid "api nu tumhehi diṭṭhaṃ vā sutaṃ vā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘macchiko macchabandho macche vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamāno tena kammena "
"tena ājīvena hatthiyāyī vā assayāyī vā rathayāyī vā yānayāyī vā bhogabhogī "
"vā mahantaṃ vā bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasanto’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.4"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.5"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.6"
msgid "Mayāpi kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, neva diṭṭhaṃ na sutaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.7"
msgid ""
"‘macchiko macchabandho macche vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamāno tena kammena "
"tena ājīvena hatthiyāyī vā assayāyī vā rathayāyī vā yānayāyī vā bhogabhogī "
"vā mahantaṃ vā bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasanto’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:2.8"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: vadhāyupanīte → vadhāyopanīte (bj) | vadhāyānīte (s1-3, km) | vadhāya nīte (mr)
msgctxt "an6.18:2.9"
msgid ""
"Te hi so, bhikkhave, macche vajjhe vadhāyupanīte pāpakena manasānupekkhati, "
"tasmā so neva hatthiyāyī hoti na assayāyī na rathayāyī na yānayāyī na "
"bhogabhogī, na mahantaṃ bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an6.18:3.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.2"
msgid "api nu tumhehi diṭṭhaṃ vā sutaṃ vā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.3"
msgid ""
"‘goghātako gāvo vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamāno tena kammena tena ājīvena "
"hatthiyāyī vā assayāyī vā rathayāyī vā yānayāyī vā bhogabhogī vā mahantaṃ vā "
"bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasanto’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.4"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.5"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.6"
msgid "Mayāpi kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, neva diṭṭhaṃ na sutaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.7"
msgid ""
"‘goghātako gāvo vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamāno tena kammena tena ājīvena "
"hatthiyāyī vā assayāyī vā rathayāyī vā yānayāyī vā bhogabhogī vā mahantaṃ vā "
"bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasanto’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.8"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:3.9"
msgid ""
"Te hi so, bhikkhave, gāvo vajjhe vadhāyupanīte pāpakena manasānupekkhati, "
"tasmā so neva hatthiyāyī hoti na assayāyī na rathayāyī na yānayāyī na "
"bhogabhogī, na mahantaṃ bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.303"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an6.18:4.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.2"
msgid "api nu tumhehi diṭṭhaṃ vā sutaṃ vā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.3"
msgid "‘orabbhiko … pe …"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sūkariko → sokariko (s1-3)
msgctxt "an6.18:4.4"
msgid "sūkariko … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.5"
msgid "sākuṇiko … pe …"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: mage → mige (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.18:4.6"
msgid ""
"māgaviko mage vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamāno tena kammena tena ājīvena "
"hatthiyāyī vā assayāyī vā rathayāyī vā yānayāyī vā bhogabhogī vā mahantaṃ vā "
"bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasanto’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.7"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.8"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhave."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.9"
msgid "Mayāpi kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, neva diṭṭhaṃ na sutaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.10"
msgid ""
"‘māgaviko mage vadhitvā vadhitvā vikkiṇamāno tena kammena tena ājīvena "
"hatthiyāyī vā assayāyī vā rathayāyī vā yānayāyī vā bhogabhogī vā mahantaṃ vā "
"bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasanto’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.11"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.12"
msgid ""
"Te hi so, bhikkhave, mage vajjhe vadhāyupanīte pāpakena manasānupekkhati, "
"tasmā so neva hatthiyāyī hoti na assayāyī na rathayāyī na yānayāyī na "
"bhogabhogī, na mahantaṃ bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: nāma → idaṃ padaṃ bahūsu
#. VAR: manasānupekkhamāno → tasmā so (s1-3, mr)
#. VAR: bhavissati → hoti (s1-3, mr)
#. VAR: ajjhāvasissati → ajjhāvasati (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "an6.18:4.13"
msgid ""
"Te hi nāma so, bhikkhave, tiracchānagate pāṇe vajjhe vadhāyupanīte pāpakena "
"manasānupekkhamāno neva hatthiyāyī bhavissati na assayāyī na rathayāyī na "
"yānayāyī na bhogabhogī, na mahantaṃ bhogakkhandhaṃ ajjhāvasissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.14"
msgid ""
"Ko pana vādo yaṃ manussabhūtaṃ vajjhaṃ vadhāyupanītaṃ pāpakena "
"manasānupekkhati."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: Tañhi tassa → taṃ hissa (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an6.18:4.15"
msgid "Tañhi tassa, bhikkhave, hoti dīgharattaṃ ahitāya dukkhāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an6.18:4.16"
msgid ""
"Kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.18:4.17"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
